		<h2>PRESS CENTRE</h2><p>Welcome to the GSA Press Centre.  The Press Centre enables members of the media to download  current and archived press releases and images for publication.  </p><p>The GSA Press Centre is managed by the Press Officer, part of the Marketing and Development, dealing with the promotion of key and strategic issues and events at The Glasgow School of Art.  The Press Officer is also the first point of contact for enquiries from members of the press and can be contacted on +44 (0) 141 353 4443 or <a href="mailto:press@gsa.ac.uk" target="">press@gsa.ac.uk</a>. </p><p><b>Key Resources for Press and Media Contacts</b></p><ul><li>Current press release </li><li>Archived press releases</li><li>Image Bank </li><li>Directory of Experts </li></ul>
	

	

	

	

	

	

	
	
	
	
	


	
	








